Title: Aliyah
Plot: Ziva's homecoming to Israel with Gibbs and the team is not a happy reunion with her father, the enigmatic and powerful head of Mossad. As tensions rise, Gibbs is forced to make a decision that sends shock waves through NCIS.
GuestStars: Arnold Vosloo, Omid Abtahi, Merik Tadros, Michael Nouri
